Class.name: Custom.SWARH.HIPS.ws.v1.q3.Attachment
Class.Description: <summary> Represents an attachment to a CDA document. The namespace of this class must stay as HIPS.PcehrSchemas for compatibility with the legacy PCEHRService that does not have separate DTO classes. </summary> Created from: http://sahipsh00.swarh.net:50500/HIPSServer_TEST/HIPS.Service.PCEHRService.svc?xsd=xsd5

Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the contents of the attached file. </summary>

Property.name: FileName
Property.Description: <summary> Gets or sets the name of the attached file. For example "XRAY.PNG" or "DOCUMENT.PDF". </summary>
